---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Personal Trainers — Client Testimonials That Fill Your Calendar | SocialProof" description="Personal trainers: collect transformation testimonials that make prospects believe they can achieve results too. Build the social proof that books consultations.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Personal Trainers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Fitness prospects are overwhelmed with options and undercut by doubt. They're not asking "is personal training worth it?" — they're asking "will it work for someone like me?" Client transformation testimonials answer that question and convert hesitation into booked consultations.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The psychology of fitness testimonials</h2>
      <p>A before-and-after photo inspires but doesn't convince. A testimonial that says "I've tried 4 trainers and nothing stuck until this — two years later I haven't quit once" creates belief. Personal trainers who lead with specific, honest client stories fill their calendars faster than those who lead with credentials and certifications.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Testimonial angles that book personal training consultations</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> "Still training 18 months later. First time I've ever stuck with anything fitness-related."</li>
        <li><strong>Starting from zero:</strong> "I hadn't exercised in 10 years. He met me exactly where I was, no judgment."</li>
        <li><strong>Busy schedules:</strong> "He works around my crazy work schedule. 45-minute sessions that actually fit into my life."</li>
        <li><strong>Post-injury:</strong> "After my back surgery, she knew exactly how to build strength without re-injury. Changed my life."</li>
        <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> "The check-ins between sessions kept me honest. That's worth the price alone."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Display testimonials where it counts</h2>
      <p>Put your best testimonial on your consultation booking page — right next to the "book a free session" button. When someone is seconds away from committing, a genuine client story removes the last hesitation. SocialProof lets you embed a scrolling testimonial widget anywhere on your site in under 5 minutes.</p>

      <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:3rem;text-align:center;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Fill your training calendar with social proof</h2>
        <p style="color:#555;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card required.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.9rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;">Get Started Free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
